Hi Mostapha

Try to replace

if ($windoz) {
my $tmploc = `echo \%TMP\%`;
chomp($tmploc);
...

with

if ($windoz) {
if (exists $ENV{'TMP'}) {
my $tmploc = $ENV{'TMP'};
} else {
my $tmploc = "C:\\Windows\\Temp";
}
chomp($tmploc);
...


Warning: Untested!

Regards,
Thomas

